{"tid":1163184,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"網民東京發現梁朝偉嘆茶 走漏眼對面係張學友","createTime":"2019-05-20T09:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T13:25:50.000Z","uid":41343,"like":10,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c729f3e8401193dd59a04951733c6e1658177c35","tid":1163184,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:47:52.000Z","msg":"一直處於休息狀態的梁朝偉，早前他太太兼經理人劉嘉玲表示，終於有劇本吸引到偉仔了，如成事的話將於這兩個月開工。<br />\n<br />\n至於偉仔的近況如何，原來他去了日本東京，今日有女網民在微博貼相，她在當地一間日式茶店碰到偉仔。難得遇上男神，女網民靜靜地偷拍了偉仔，還刻意與偉仔遠距離來張合照，該女網民留言︰「出來喝茶偶遇男神坐我旁邊桌，想想表（別）打擾人家，默默偷拍幾張算了。」相中的偉仔精神不錯，與坐對面的友人有說有笑。後來女網民再留言表示，好像被發現偷拍，她留言︰「好像被發現偷拍了，對不起啊，我忍不住不拍啊，實在太nice了。」<br />\n<br />\n不過最搞笑的是，該女網民只被偉仔吸引住，完全沒留意與偉仔一齊喝茶、坐對面的友人正是張學友，該女網民後悔的說︰「最搞笑的是喝完茶，我站起來走了，最後回頭看一眼才發現，坐他對面的人，居然是張學友，來不及偷拍了。」而該女網民形容學友看起來很瘦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190519/large/1558269302_4538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190519%2Flarge%2F1558269302_4538.jpg&h=5a18c180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190519/large/1558269302_98ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190519%2Flarge%2F1558269302_98ae.jpg&h=f6f588d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190519/large/1558269305_bdef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190519%2Flarge%2F1558269305_bdef.jpg&h=a052e4c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36968df90a6dd27db8c0b81dd819baa00b3a56e3","tid":1163184,"uid":75610,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"這些機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad68729bd2be75baa41197f62663443d585c4e94","tid":1163184,"uid":41343,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:50:05.000Z","msg":"又有網友捕獲他們在六本木的一間居酒屋出現，同樣見到梁朝偉對住張學友雞啄唔斷，但令人最驚喜的，是竟然張學友的太太羅美薇也在場！上載該短片的網民笑言能拍得「阿飛」梁朝偉及「阿基」張學友已難得，想不到更拍得神隱多時的羅美薇。雖然片中因角度問題，未能清楚見到張學友和羅美薇的樣子，但羅美薇一如以往，在公眾場合戴口罩，保持低調外，其他網民指梁朝偉見到張學友尤如開籠雀：「跟老張在一起就變話癆」、「羅美薇好年輕漂亮啊！像四十歲！」戴住口罩都睇到？勁！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190519/photo/bkn-20190519232947751-0519_00862_001_06p.jpg?20190520000736\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190519%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190519232947751-0519_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20190520000736&h=60ac9d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190519/photo/bkn-20190519232947751-0519_00862_001_07p.jpg?20190520000736\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190519%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190519232947751-0519_00862_001_07p.jpg%3F20190520000736&h=e189f84e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ad84c9a56885ab7c27c3ba8ba670238e7bfa552","tid":1163184,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ffdf765b0ba0556766f98e00d7f47f3ec04abd","tid":1163184,"uid":82917,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa